abstract:
The objective of this research is to demonstrate a mathematical technique to analyze the Covid-19 outbreak, particularly with respect to Malaysia. The technique is able to accommodate scarcity, quantity, and availability of the data set. The obtained results can offer descriptive insight for reflecting and strategizing actions in combating the pandemic.
Competing Interest Statement
author: Wan Munirah Wan Mohamad; Tahir Ahmad; Amirul Aizad Ahmad Fuad; Nurfarhana Hassan; Siti Rahmah Awang; Azmirul Ashaari; Siti Salwana Mamat
title: Fuzzy Autocatalytic analysis of Covid-19 outbreak in Malaysia
